t between end-users' top feature\nrequests and Android developers' responses, particularly for the more recent\nAndroid releases. Our findings suggest that effort spent responding to\nend-users' loudest calls may be integral to software systems' survival, and a\nproduct's overall success.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Mar 2021 02:17:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-15"}
