erving and $CP$ violating solutions are\nallowed in the model. Interesting correlations are obtained, specially, between\nYukawa couplings of modular weight 2 and complex modulus $\\tau$. The model\nexhibit consistent explanation of BAU for right-handed Majorana neutrino mass\nscale in the range ($(1-5)\\times10^{13}$)GeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Mar 2021 10:59:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 09:18:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-04"}
